Cinnamon Miles is the co-founder and lead designer at Liberty Jane Clothing, a company she co-founded in 2008 by selling a single item on eBay. Cinnamon is also an official Brand Ambassador for Bernina, the world's premiere sewing machine company.
Liberty Jane Clothing, with over 200,000 digital guidebooks downloaded, and thousands of raving fans, has become a powerful brand in their small niche. Cinnamon's One Of A Kind doll clothes regularly sell at auction for over $200 with her highest auction ending at over $335.
The company uses social media extensively and has more than 9,000 subscribers on Youtube, (with over 1.6 million video views), more than 24,000 Fans in Facebook, and more than 5,000 followers on Pinterest.
Using the power of social media Liberty Jane Clothing has become a thriving six figure online business. Cinnamon also co-founder The Cutting Room, a membership community for like-minded craft business owners.
